    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "my bad, i thought u had the git hook integrated. here's the gist of the changes in #402:\n\n- remove /src/orchestrator/agent_runtime/ (this handles all long-running agent loops)\n- replace agent_loop() with stateless event-driven triggers in AWS Lambda\n- deprecate AgentCore class and its session management logic\n- goal: reduce compute overhead by 85% by moving away from persistent agentic states\n\nit basically moves us to a model where we don't run active agents anymore, just quick tasks. lmk if this looks like it'll break any current workflows in the repo.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
